---
import OleloPhrase from "./ui/OleloPhrase.astro";
import HawaiianIslands from "./HawaiianIslands.astro";
---
<section id="top" class="relative isolate overflow-hidden hero-halo pt-28 md:pt-36 pb-16 md:pb-24">
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 paper-noise opacity-60"></div>

  <div class="container-x relative">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs md:text-[0.78rem] uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-lava mb-6 fade-up">
        <span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-lava align-middle mr-2"></span>
        A Hawai‘i 501(c)(3) · Papaikou, Hawai‘i Island
      </p>

      <h1 class="font-display font-medium text-display-lg md:text-display-xl leading-[0.95] tracking-tight text-ink fade-up"
          style="text-wrap: balance; animation-delay: 60ms;">
        There’s a person<br/>
        <span class="italic text-lava" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144;">at the window.</span>
        We tell their story.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-7 max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl text-stone leading-relaxed fade-up" style="animation-delay: 140ms;">
        The Hawaii Mobile Food Foundation is a long-form podcast, a marketing curriculum
        being built for vendors, and the small advocacy work that goes with both —
        in service of the people who feed Hawai‘i out of a window.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3 fade-up" style="animation-delay: 220ms;">
        <a href="#podcast" class="btn btn-donor !py-4 !px-7 text-base">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M8 7l5 3-5 3z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
          Listen to the podcast
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#vendors" class="btn btn-ghost !py-4 !px-7 text-base">
          I run a truck
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 fade-up" style="animation-delay: 320ms;">
        <OleloPhrase haw="ʻAʻohe hana nui ke alu ʻia" en="No task is too big when done together." />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 md:mt-20 fade-up" style="animation-delay: 420ms;">
      <HawaiianIslands class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto h-auto float-slow" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
